OL,3,CTasty offer for Kellogg's staff to
OL,4,Cfinish work early on Fridays
OL,6,FHundreds of employees at a cereal and
OL,7,Fsnacks firm are being offered the
OL,8,Fchance to finish work early on Fridays
OL,9,Fas part of a popular summer hours
OL,10,Fscheme.
OL,12,FKellanova, which owns Kellogg's and
OL,13,FPringles, announced that staff will be
OL,14,Fable to go home from 12pm on Fridays
OL,15,Funtil September provided they have
OL,16,Fcompleted a full week's hours.
