OL,3,CTasty offer for Kellogg's staff to
OL,4,Cfinish work early on Fridays
OL,6,FThe company employs more than 500
OL,7,Fworkers at its office in MediaCity,
OL,8,FSalford, and a further 60 in its field
OL,9,Fsales team, all of whom will be
OL,10,Foffered the opportunity to take half a
OL,11,Fday a week for themselves.
OL,13,FKellanova said its research suggested
OL,14,Fthat two thirds of people would be
OL,15,Fwilling to work harder during the rest
OL,16,Fof the week if their employer gave
OL,17,Fthem Friday afternoons off.
