OL,3,CTasty offer for Kellogg's staff to
OL,4,Cfinish work early on Fridays
OL,6,FLejla Damon, Kellanova shopper
OL,7,Fmarketing manager, said: "In my spare
OL,8,Ftime, I'm training to become a yoga
OL,9,Fteacher and even run a monthly class
OL,10,Ffor my colleagues in the office.
OL,12,F"In the five years I've worked at
OL,13,FKellanova, the summer hours programme
OL,14,Fhas allowed me the time to take on
OL,15,Fextra courses as I work towards my
OL,16,Fqualification. This summer I'm looking
OL,17,Fforward to teaching a few additional
OL,18,Fclasses with my Friday afternoons."
