OL,3,CTasty offer for Kellogg's staff to
OL,4,Cfinish work early on Fridays
OL,6,FChris Silcock, managing director of
OL,7,FKellanova, said: "Our summer hours
OL,8,Fprogramme has been running for more
OL,9,Fthan two decades now but it's still
OL,10,Fsuch a great benefit for our teams.
OL,12,F"I know how hard everyone works
OL,13,Fthroughout the week, so to be able to
OL,14,Fgive people half a day for themselves
OL,15,Freally helps them to recharge and
OL,16,Fimproves productivity."
